{"type":"message","id":"5aa6cf89","parentId":"eda5755f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:26:40.753Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:dc676ffd-0c3d-470b-9a6d-93e3c01dfcc8 A股竞价模式筛选] 执行A股竞价模式筛选任务。\n\n背景：这是交易日早上9:25，开盘前筛选。\n\n步骤：\n1. 确定今日日期和前一交易日（如果是周一，则取上周五）。用以下Python获取：\n```python\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ntoday_dt = datetime.strptime(today, '%Y%m%d')\nif today_dt.weekday() == 0:\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=3)\nelse:\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=1)\nprev_date = prev_dt.strftime('%Y%m%d')\n```\n\n2. 获取前一交易日涨停数据：\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='YYYYMMDD')\n```\n\n3. 对涨停股逐只获取K线数据（用BaoStock），计算：\n   - 连板数(lb)\n   - 量比(vr)\n   - RSI、MACD状态\n   - 趋势、MA20/MA60位置\n\n4. 使用 auction_ok 函数判断竞价条件：\n```python\nfrom auction import auction_ok\nok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning = auction_ok(code, name, lb, jb_prob, vr, sector_hot, phase)\n```\n\n5. 筛选出符合竞价模式的股票（ok_min <= 8 and vr >= 0.5）\n\n6. 计算预测晋级成功率（使用 predict_stock 函数）\n\n7. 生成飞书报告，格式如下（注意：飞书不支持Markdown表格，用纯文本空格对齐格式）：\n\n【📈 竞价模式筛选】日期：YYYYMMDD（前一交易日YYYYMMDD复盘）\n\n市场情绪：[从涨停数量、炸板率判断]\n筛选股票数：X只\n\n【✅ 重点竞价】\n\n代码/名称        板位  晋级%   竞价区间    量比   板块\n-------------------------------------------------\n000001 某股票    3板   23.2%   1.5~4.5%   1.19   电力\n\n【晋级概率分布】\n- >30%：X只\n- 15-30%：X只\n- <15%：X只\n\n【板块联动】（有板块效应的列出）\n- XX板块：X只（竞价池X只）\n\n【操作建议】\n- 激进型：股票名(X%)、股票名(X%)\n- 稳健型：股票名(X%)、股票名(X%)\n\n⚠️ 注意：市场处于[阶段]期，晋级概率整体[偏高/偏低]，竞价需严格控制。实际结果受市场情绪影响较大，谨慎操作。\n\n8. 用message工具发送到飞书：user:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0，标题「📈 竞价模式筛选 YYMMDD」\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 9:26 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 01:26 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774229200749}}
