{"type":"message","id":"ae287fc4","parentId":"18362570","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:29:27.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see all VR values are 1.00, which seems suspicious. The VR calculation might be incorrect. Also, the 晋级概率 values are all very low (mostly under 10%), which could be correct for a \"退潮\" (ebbing/tide-out) market phase. Let me analyze the data more carefully and also look at why VR is always 1.00.\n\nLet me now also check the data for what the market sentiment looks like, and then filter by the auction criteria: `ok_min <= 8 and vr >= 0.5`. Since all VR=1.00, they all pass the vr >= 0.5 criteria. But let me filter for `ok_min <= 8` which they all pass (ok_min is 1.0~3.0).\n \nLooking at the auction_ok conditions more carefully, the selection criteria `ok_min <= 8 and vr >= 0.5` seems too permissive given these numbers. I should examine the actual market sentiment first—whether we're in an ebb phase—and then apply more selective filtering to identify which stocks truly qualify for the auction pattern.\n\nThe晋级概率 values are uniformly low (mostly 1-11%), which aligns with the 退潮 market phase. Now I'll focus on the sector analysis and how the 电力 sector is performing in this environment.","thinkingSignature":"67faac44cfcf81650774d084b78e0e556d4415be041951308f26629ca2cadc97"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rb153jthpw83_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock')\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace')\n\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n# 获取昨日涨停池来评估市场情绪\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='20260320')\nzt_df_prev = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='20260319') if False else None  # 跳过，避免重复请求\n\n# 炸板数据\ntry:\n    zd_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_fh_pool_em(date='20260320')\n    print(f\"昨日炸板股数量: {len(zd_df)}\")\nexcept:\n    zd_df = pd.DataFrame()\n\n# 昨日涨停数量对比\nprint(f\"今日（昨日复盘）涨停: {len(zt_df)}\")\n\n# 按连板数分组\nprint(\"\\n连板分布:\")\nprint(zt_df.groupby('连板数').size().sort_index())\n\n# 按行业统计\nprint(\"\\n行业分布:\")\nsector_counts = zt_df.groupby('所属行业').size().sort_values(ascending=False)\nprint(sector_counts.head(10))\n\n# 电力板块\ndl = zt_df[zt_df['所属行业'] == '电力']\nprint(f\"\\n电力板块: {len(dl)}只\")\nprint(dl[['代码','名称','连板数']].to_string())\n\n# 判断市场阶段\ntotal_zt = len(zt_df)\nif total_zt >= 50:\n    phase = \"发酵\"\n    sentiment = \"极热\"\nelif total_zt >= 30:\n    phase = \"启动\"\n    sentiment = \"偏热\"\nelif total_zt >= 15:\n    phase = \"正常\"\n    sentiment = \"中性\"\nelif total_zt >= 8:\n    phase = \"退潮\"\n    sentiment = \"偏冷\"\nelse:\n    phase = \"冰点\"\n    sentiment = \"极冷\"\n\nprint(f\"\\n市场阶段判断: {phase}（{sentiment}）\")\nprint(f\"涨停数量: {total_zt}\")\n\n# 检查板块联动\nsector_hot_threshold = 3\nhot_sectors = sector_counts[sector_counts >= sector_hot_threshold]\nprint(f\"\\n板块联动（≥{sector_hot_threshold}只）:\")\nfor sector, count in hot_sectors.items():\n    print(f\"  {sector}: {count}只\")\nPYEOF","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12710,"output":851,"cacheRead":27169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774229347981}}
