{"type":"message","id":"47ec8808","parentId":"6557f389","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:31:26.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the data. Let me now generate the report and send it to Feishu.\n\nKey data:\n- Date: 20260323 (竞价 for March 23 trading day, based on March 20 复盘)\n- Market sentiment: 正常（中性）- 28只涨停\n- 晋级概率分布: >30%: 0只, 15-30%: 10只, <15%: 17只\n- 板块联动: 电力 7只, 光伏设备 4只\n- 重点竞价: \n  - 600617 国新能源 LB2 Prob=28.2%\n  - 603165 荣晟环保 LB1 Prob=24.0%\n  - 000601 韶能股份 LB3 Prob=23.2%\n  - 002428 云南锗业 LB1 Prob=20.3%\n  - 002150 正泰电源 LB1 Prob=19.2%\n  - 000862 银星能源 LB1 Prob=19.2%\n\nI'm seeing several stocks with strong晋级 probabilities in the 15-30% range, particularly in the power and small metals sectors, which could be worth focusing on for the report.\n\nLooking at the remaining candidates, I notice the solar equipment stocks like 603381 永臻股份 and the power sector plays like 东方新能 and 华电能源 all fall into that same 17-18% probability range. There's also a notably weaker candidate with 大胜达 at 16.6%. For riskier positions, I'm considering 恒天海龙, 福然德, and 美诺华 which have lower probabilities around 12-13%, while also noting that high-board positions like 深华发Ａ and 华电辽能 are coming in with extremely low晋级 rates under 2%.\n\nSince the overall market is showing neutral conditions with晋级 probabilities tilted toward the lower end, I'm going to construct the report by pulling the top performers across different probability brackets to give a balanced view of the opportunities.","thinkingSignature":"1a879b22b30023ffbdfac44627a2cd2a5f4bd83984dc2283882e8af53a98883f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fdz7fs84yv79_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /tmp/auction_results.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\n# 筛选qualified的\nq = [r for r in data if r['qualify']]\nq.sort(key=lambda x: x['jb_prob'], reverse=True)\n\n# 激进型（高概率+高板位）\n# 稳健型（中概率，较低板位）\naggressive = [r for r in q if r['jb_prob'] >= 15 and r['lb'] >= 2][:5]\nconservative = [r for r in q if r['jb_prob'] >= 10 and r['lb'] == 1][:5]\n\nprint('激进型:')\nfor r in aggressive:\n    print(f'  {r[\\\"code\\\"]} {r[\\\"name\\\"]} LB{r[\\\"lb\\\"]} Prob={r[\\\"jb_prob\\\"]}% Range={r[\\\"ok_min\\\"]}~{r[\\\"ok_max\\\"]}%')\nprint('稳健型:')\nfor r in conservative:\n    print(f'  {r[\\\"code\\\"]} {r[\\\"name\\\"]} LB{r[\\\"lb\\\"]} Prob={r[\\\"jb_prob\\\"]}% Range={r[\\\"ok_min\\\"]}~{r[\\\"ok_max\\\"]}%')\n\"\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17125,"output":723,"cacheRead":27169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774229433031}}
